column4: I've tried two wireless network cards and i've reinstalled ubuntu 9.04 but my wireless card won't scan the green LED is on in the back but when I use iwlist scan it says wlan1 no results
it was working like a week ago but then stopped working . Once i booted up in a live CD yesterday and it worked but when i restarted it won't work anymore ...
network-manager finds my card but it just won't show any networks in the area
